snippet.title: Goldspace - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore a dying galaxy in this story-driven, high-octane twin stick shooter. Upgrade your arsenal and gun your way through reactive, fully destructible environments. 
Play it for free on https://goldspacegame.com
Join the community: https://discord.gg/XukUBzs
